  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC421">
        <l>uyartiṇai maruṅki ṉummait tokaiyē</l>
	<l>palarcoṉ ṉaṭaitteṉa moḻimaṉār pulavar.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/211/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/212/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
<p>ic cūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, ummait tokaiyuḷ orucāraṉavaṟṟukkaṇ paṭuvatōr vēṟupāṭu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai: uyartiṇai maruṅkiṉ ummait tokaic collukku iṟuti palaraic colluñ coṉṉaṭaittāka eṉṟu collupa āciriyar eṉṟavāṟu</p>
<p>varalāṟu : kapilaparaṇar eṉa varum.</p>
<p>ivvāṟu attokaiccol liṟuti palarcoṉṉaṭaittaṉṟik kapilaṉ paraṇaṉ eṉa ṉakaravīṟāy niṟpiṉ, atu, 'vantāṉ, pōyiṉāṉ' eṉṉum oruviṉaiyēṟpiṉallatu, 'vantār, pōyiṉār' eṉṉum paṉmaiviṉai ēlā.</p>
<p>iṉip, 'palar coṉṉaṭaittu' eṉavē avviruvar mēlum viṉaiyēṟkum ; ataṉāṉ itu colliṉār eṉpatu.</p>
<p>maṟṟut tokaic coṟkaḷ tokuvatu tokku niṉṟakkāl, tammīṟu karutiṉa poruṭkēṟkum muṭiviṉai niṉṟāṅkē niṉṟu koḷḷum ; ituvāyiṉ iṟuti niṉṟāṅkē niṟpap poruṭkēṟpa muṭipu ēlāmaiyāṉ, iṟutipōtal vēṇṭiṟṟu eṉpatu.	          (25)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

